snippet.title: Introducing Menimals! (Menimals Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Introducing Menimals! An online strategy battle game for PC and Mac, collect characters and then travel the world fighting on your quest to save the world. Play in online multiplayer as well as hundreds of single player battles. You will love playing Menimals!

Available soon on Steam!
